00:45:38.649 --> 00:45:47.229
called Ultimate Block that Gloria
and I were using for table of contents,

00:45:47.739 --> 00:45:50.948
to add the table of contents to stories.

00:45:51.959 --> 00:45:55.696
They were not accessible
because screen reader

00:45:55.697 --> 00:46:01.921
did not detect which element
was turned on or off, checkboxes,

00:46:01.970 --> 00:46:03.820
radio buttons, and so on.

00:46:04.970 --> 00:46:10.778
It's always a challenge when dealing
with third-party plugins.

00:46:12.749 --> 00:46:17.405
My invitation for developers is,
please, do it accessible

00:46:17.621 --> 00:46:27.234
because it gives more chances to creators.

